name: SVGFEImageElement
description: The SVGFEImageElement interface corresponds to the <feImage> element.

members.name: SVGFEImageElement.preserveAspectRatio
members.description: An SVGAnimatedPreserveAspectRatio corresponding to the preserveAspectRatio attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEImageElement.crossOrigin
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString reflects the crossorigin attribute of the given element, limited to only known values.
